---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Network, Search, Briefcase } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="Vision | About FarmWork">
  
  <section style="min-height: 100vh; padding: 10rem 0 6rem 0; background: var(--surface-color); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
    <div class="container fade-up">
      
      {/* The Dense Bento Wall Container */}
      <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;">
        
        {/* TOP ROW: Manifesto (Span 8) */}
        <div style="grid-column: span 8; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 32px; padding: 4rem; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border); border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2rem; background: var(--bg-color); color: var(--primary); align-self: flex-start; font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
            The Core Issue
          </div>
          <h1 class="heading-xl" style="line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">
            A Massive Sector Operating <br/> Without An Engine.
          </h1>
          <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.6;">
            The unorganized agriculture segment functions on fragmented phone calls, cash economies, and sheer physical effort. The infrastructure completely breaks down at scale.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* TOP ROW: Statistic (Span 4) */}
        <div style="grid-column: span 4; background: var(--primary); border-radius: 32px; padding: 4rem; color: #fff; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
          <div style="position: absolute; top: -20%; right: -20%; width: 250px; height: 250px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%;"></div>
          
          <span style="font-size: 5.5rem; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; font-family: var(--font-heading); position: relative; z-index: 10;">140M</span>
          <span style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; position: relative; z-index: 10;">Invisible Workers</span>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.4; position: relative; z-index: 10;">Operating in India entirely without proof of work.</p>
        </div>

        {/* MID ROW: Card 1 - Farmers (Span 4) */}
        <div style="grid-column: span 4; background: var(--bg-color); border-radius: 32px; padding: 3rem; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);">
          <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 12px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <Search size={24} color="var(--primary)" />
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Farmers</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Labour shortages during narrow harvest windows lead to immense losses. Machinery is unaffordable without clustered resource sharing.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* MID ROW: Card 2 - Workers (Span 4) */}
        <div style="grid-column: span 4; background: var(--text-primary); border-radius: 32px; padding: 3rem; color: #ffffff;">
          <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <Briefcase size={24} color="#ffffff" />
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: #fff;">Workers</h3>
          <p style="color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Without a verified digital identity, labourers completely lack access to formal credit lines or farm-specific insurance pathways.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* MID ROW: Card 3 - Markets (Span 4) */}
        <div style="grid-column: span 4; background: var(--bg-color); border-radius: 32px; padding: 3rem; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);">
          <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 12px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <Network size={24} color="var(--accent)" />
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Markets</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Zero production visibility guarantees distress sales. Strong linkages necessitate verifiable output intelligence prior to arrival.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* BOT ROW: Vision Banner (Span 12) */}
        <div style="grid-column: span 12; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 32px; border: 1px solid var(--surface-border); overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative;">
          
          <div style="flex: 1; padding: 5rem 4rem; position: relative; z-index: 10;">
            <h2 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem); color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.1; font-family: var(--font-heading);">
              Building the <span style="color: var(--primary);">Digital Infrastructure</span><br/> for Rural Farm Work.
            </h2>
          </div>
          
          <div style="flex: 1; position: relative; min-height: 300px; height: 100%;">
            <img src="/media/img-6.jpeg" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: right center;" alt="Farming Panorama" />
            <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff 0%, transparent 100%);"></div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    [style*="grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr)"] > div {
      grid-column: span 12 !important;
    }
    [style*="grid-column: span 12;"] {
      flex-direction: column !important;
    }
  }
</style>
